    gg:gurmukhi "ਸਹਸ ਸਿਆਣਪਾ ਲਖ ਹੋਹਿ ਤ ਇਕ ਨ ਚਲੈ ਨਾਲਿ ॥"@pa ;
    gg:transliteration "Sahas siaṇapā lakh hoveh, ta ik na cẖalai nāl."@en-Latn ;
    gg:translation "One may possess hundreds of thousands of clever ideas, yet not even one of them will go along in the end."@en ;
    gg:hasTheme gg:Intellect,
                   gg:Ego ;
    rdfs:comment "No amount of cleverness or intellectual strategy survives death or leads to Truth by itself; intellect without surrender remains barren spiritually."@en ;
