    gg:transliteration "kiv sacẖiārā hoeeai"@en-Latn ;
    gg:translation "how can one become truthful; how to live in Truth"@en .

### Tuk 5 – GlossUnit 2: ਕਿਵ ਕੂੜੈ

gg:japji_pauri1_tuk5_gu2 a gg:GlossUnit ;
