    gg:gurmukhi "ਕਿਵ ਕੂੜੈ"@pa ;
    gg:transliteration "kiv Kūṛai"@en-Latn ;
    gg:translation "how can (this) falsehood"@en .

### Tuk 5 – GlossUnit 3: ਤੁਟੈ ਪਾਲਿ

